name: language_html_data_style_comment_closer
description: |
  Star-slash closes a surrounding CSS comment. Sanitizers that wrap untrusted
  data in comments or strip comment-looking text can expose following bytes to
  the CSS parser.
format: utf8-strip
decode-as: ascii
tags:
  - "language"
  - "html"
  - "xss"
  - "xss-data"
  - "style-context"
  - "css"
  - "comment-closer"
  - "parser-state"
---
*/
